    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Comparison Report: UT/EAC\"\nauthor: \"Ali Al-Timimi, PhD\"\nformat: html\nparams:\n  data_file: \"C:/Users/drziy/OneDrive/Desktop/Ali/scientific_research_current/global-cancer-complexity/output/global_cancer/RData/comparison_data/comparison_data_ut_eac.rds\"\nexecute:\n  eval: true\n---\n\n\n\n::: {.panel-tabset}\n\n### UT/EAC Overview\n\n::: {.panel-tabset}\n\n#### Probes\n> -   **Cancer Category:** carcinomas\n> -   **Chip hu35ksuba**: 386 filtered probes\n> -   **Chip hu6800**: 81 filtered probes\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](../../resources/plots/probes/ut_eac_probe_counts.png){width=7in}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n#### Summary Assessment\n\n**Overall Complexity & Entropy Assessment**\n\n| Measure | All Filtered Probes | GO MF Terms | KEGG Pathways | HALLMARK Genes |\n|:---|:---|:---|:---|:---|\n| **Complexity** | not available | strong gain (uncertain) | strong loss (uncertain) | strong gain (moderately supported) |\n| **Shannon Entropy** | not available | no clear change (moderately supported) | no clear change (uncertain) | no clear change (uncertain) |\n| **Spectral Entropy** | not available | strongly anti-chaotic (moderately supported) | mildly anti-chaotic (uncertain) | mildly anti-chaotic (uncertain) |\n\n::: {.callout-note}\n**Interpretation Guide**\n\n- **Gain** = Increased complexity from normal to tumor\n- **Loss** = Complexity reduction from normal to tumor\n- **Chaotic** = Increased entropy from normal to tumor\n- **Anti-Chaotic** = Entropy reduction from normal to tumor\n- **P-values** = All p-values unadjusted unless noted\n:::\n\n:::\n\n### GO Biological Process Clusters\n\n::: {.panel-tabset}\n\n#### Complexity Change\n\n<h4>Gain Complexity Clusters</h4>\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-hover table-condensed\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;\"> Cluster </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> # Terms </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> p-value </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;\"> Representative Terms </th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 6 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 1 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.021 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> nervous system development </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 11 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 1 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.045 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> positive regulation of apoptotic process </td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n<tfoot>\n<tr>\n<td style = 'padding: 0; border:0;' colspan='100%'><sup>*</sup> Combined p-values are computed using Fisher’s method (sumlog) across the GO terms in each cluster.</td>\n</tr>\n</tfoot>\n</table>\n<h4>Loss Complexity Clusters</h4>\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-hover table-condensed\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;\"> Cluster </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> # Terms </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> p-value </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;\"> Representative Terms </th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 13 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 3 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.859 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> positive regulation of transcription, DNA-templated; positive regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II; positive regulation of transcription, DNA-templated </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 1 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 3 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.861 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> negative regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II; regulation of transcription, DNA-templated; regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II </td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n<tfoot>\n<tr>\n<td style = 'padding: 0; border:0;' colspan='100%'><sup>*</sup> Combined p-values are computed using Fisher’s method (sumlog) across the GO terms in each cluster.</td>\n</tr>\n</tfoot>\n</table>\n\n#### Spectral Entropy Change\n\n⚠️ Table not available.\n\n:::\n\n### GO Molecular Function Terms\n\n::: {.panel-tabset}\n\n#### Complexity Change\n\n**Significant GO Molecular Function Terms (Complexity)**\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](../../resources/plots/go/ut_eac_go_complexity.png){width=7in}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n<h4>Gained Complexity</h4>\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-hover table-condensed\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;\"> GeneSet </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> p-value </th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> chromatin binding </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.050 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> endocytosis </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.050 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> extracellular matrix organization </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.050 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> mitotic cell cycle </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.030 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> protein binding </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.020 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> transmembrane transport </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.000 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> ubiquitin protein ligase binding </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.020 </td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4>Lost Complexity</h4>\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-hover table-condensed\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;\"> GeneSet </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> p-value </th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> cell division </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.010 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> positive regulation of gene expression </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.040 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> protein homodimerization activity </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.050 </td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n#### Spectral Entropy Change\n\n**Significant GO Molecular Function Terms (Spectral Entropy)**\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](../../resources/plots/go/ut_eac_go_entropy.png){width=7in}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n<h4>Strongly Anti-Chaotic</h4>\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-hover table-condensed\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;\"> GeneSet </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> p-value </th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> GTPase activity </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.010 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> RNA polymerase II cis-regulatory region sequence-specific DNA binding </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.030 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> cell-cell adhesion mediator activity </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.000 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> cytoskeleton organization </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.030 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> gene expression </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.010 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> glucose homeostasis </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.020 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> homophilic cell adhesion via plasma membrane adhesion molecules </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.000 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> negative regulation of gene expression </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.000 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> nervous system development </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.000 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> neuron differentiation </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.000 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> positive regulation of cell population proliferation </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.000 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> positive regulation of cell population proliferation </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.050 </td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h4>Mildly Anti-Chaotic</h4>\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-hover table-condensed\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;\"> GeneSet </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> p-value </th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> G protein-coupled receptor signaling pathway </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.030 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> cadherin binding </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.040 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> cell adhesion </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.030 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> establishment of protein localization </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.020 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> ion transmembrane transport </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.000 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> ion transport </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.040 </td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h4>Mildly Chaotic</h4>\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-hover table-condensed\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;\"> GeneSet </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> p-value </th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> ATP binding </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.030 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> cell-cell adhesion </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.000 </td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n:::\n\n### KEGG Pathway Analysis\n\n::: {.panel-tabset}\n\n#### Complexity Change\n\n**Significant KEGG Pathways (Complexity)**\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}\n\n```\n⚠️ Plot not available.\n```\n\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n<h4>Lost Complexity</h4>\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-hover table-condensed\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;\"> GeneSet </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> p-value </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:center;\"> Cancer Pathway </th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> Pathways in cancer </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.340 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> ✅ </td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n#### Spectral Entropy Change\n\n**Significant KEGG Pathways (Spectral Entropy)**\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](../../resources/plots/kegg/ut_eac_kegg_entropy.png){width=7in}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n<h4>Mildly Anti-Chaotic</h4>\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-hover table-condensed\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;\"> GeneSet </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> p-value </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:center;\"> Cancer Pathway </th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> Pathways in cancer </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.620 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> ✅ </td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h4>Mildly Chaotic</h4>\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-hover table-condensed\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;\"> GeneSet </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> p-value </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:center;\"> Cancer Pathway </th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> Calcium signaling pathway </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.050 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\">  </td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n:::\n\n### HALLMARK Genes Analysis\n\n::: {.panel-tabset}\n\n#### Complexity Change\n\n**Significant HALLMARK Genes (Complexity)**\n\n<h4>Gained Complexity</h4>\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-hover table-condensed\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;\"> GeneSet </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> p-value </th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> HALLMARK_E2F_TARGETS </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 0.040 </td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n#### Spectral Entropy Change\n\n**Significant HALLMARK Genes (Spectral Entropy)**\n\nNo significant MSigDB gene sets found (spectral entropy).\n\n:::\n\n### Latent Geometry\n\n**Latent-space normal-versus-tumor summary**\n\nLatent-space metrics are computed from the VAE representation using samples derived from the **hu35ksuba** platform only. These quantities summarize within-class geometric structure and separation between normal and tumor states in the learned latent space.\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n\n|Measure             | Normal|  Tumor|  Delta|\n|:-------------------|------:|------:|------:|\n|Participation ratio |  1.407|  3.804|  2.397|\n|Eigenvalue entropy  |  0.584|  1.532|  0.948|\n|Anisotropy          |  0.834|  0.406| -0.429|\n|Radius              | 23.443| 28.415|  4.972|\n|Centroid distance   | 26.499|     NA|     NA|\n\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n:::\n",
